<BR>
Here's soem more info on the gloves:<BR>
<BR>
First of all Honesty is right. Quoting here:<BR>
<BR>
: Honesty 2000-05-05 22:00:52 <BR>
Aussum AC but, I must say as a Cleric that the Effect: Reckless Strength is not very good (I got it at level 5) and I tried using it when I first got it but have not had it memmed since. The reason it stinks is that it gives like +20 strength at first but then it slowly decreases and continues decreasing until you are -20 Strength and we all know -20 strength is no good. However, I believe you can cancel the icon once cast if it is on yourself but not if the effect is cast on another (they will be stuck with it..and hopefully, they wont get mad at you when they see their strength going into the negatives) <BR>
<BR>
- They come off the Drolvarg Captain in Karnor's Castle. He is located on the first balcony you see of the castle when you enter the zone. You can acess the area by going right up the stairs which are located in the right side of the castle after the first bridge.<BR>
<BR>
- They look like dark grey-very dark blue plate <BR>
<BR>
- The AC is of couse fantastic but the effect is completely awful since it also takes about 5-6 secs to be casted and the actual effect as Honesty says above is disapointing. You can casted it on others but its not worth it overal.<BR>
<BR>
Hope this helps<BR>
<BR>
Duncan<BR>
